item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

Jagex cant shut moparscape down. Moparscape has never broken any of Jagex’s compnay and RuneScape polocies. If they did, they would have been gone by now. Also IT IS IMPOSSIBLE TO TRANSFER ACCOUNTS because moparscape is just a private server being run by a small community of pre-java coders. There is no way to access a runescape account to manually edit it or replace it with a moparscape account. Plus moparscape accounts are probably much differently coded then rs accounts because moparscape is a lot less experience-filled then runescape is…
